source code fro file and directly pollers and associated test cases&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12420779" author="bayard" created="Thu, 13 Jul 2006 10:24:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Surprised we&apos;ve not got pollers already. Definite +1 for 1.3.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12441477" author="h2o" created="Wed, 11 Oct 2006 15:16:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be incredibly useful if this functionality could make optional use of an alternative backend, e.g. &lt;a href=&quot;http://jnotify.sourceforge.net/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jnotify.sourceforge.net/&lt;/a&gt;. By default the Java mechanisms can be used but having a pluggable &quot;event provider&quot; abstraction interface would be nice.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12463667" author="bayard" created="Wed, 10 Jan 2007 18:45:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Quartz contains a FileScanJob that is a poller - so possibly it might be better to point people to that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
